msgstr "Intelligent issue analysis via AI: editorial draft, innovation radar, SDG impact, and global collaboration map."

msgid "plugins.generic.issueSpotlight.detailedDescription"
msgstr "This module uses artificial intelligence to generate advanced analysis perspectives:<ul style=\"margin-top:5px; padding-left:20px;\"><li><strong>Editorial Summary:</strong> Automatic draft of an editorial summarizing key themes.</li><li><strong>Innovation Radar:</strong> Visual map of emerging and consolidated technological trends.</li><li><strong>SDG Impact:</strong> Assessment of thematic alignment with the UN Sustainable Development Goals.</li><li><strong>Global Map:</strong> Visualization of the geographical distribution of authors and international collaboration networks.</li></ul>"

